OL,3,CHundreds of prisoners released early
OL,4,Cin Scotland
OL,6,FNearly 400 prisoners are being
OL,7,Freleased early as the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment continues to tackle
OL,9,Fovercrowding in the country's prisons.
OL,11,FThe release point has changed for
OL,12,Fthose serving jail time of less than
OL,13,Ffour years - from 50% of their
OL,14,Fsentence to 40% - in an emergency move
OL,15,Fby MSPs in November 2024.
OL,17,FIt's expected the change will reduce
OL,18,Fthe prison population by 5%, according
OL,19,Fto the Scottish Government.
