OL,3,CHundreds of prisoners released early
OL,4,Cin Scotland
OL,6,FUp to 390 prisoners will be released
OL,7,Fin three stages, with the first
OL,8,Fstarting on 18 February and ending on
OL,9,F20 February 2025.
OL,11,FThe other times of release will take
OL,12,Fplace from 4 to 6 March and the 18 to
OL,13,F20 March 2025.
OL,15,FDomestic abuse or sexual offenders
OL,16,Fwill not be released early under the
OL,17,Fchanges.
OL,19,FJustice Secretary Angela Constance
OL,20,Fsaid the early releases were needed to
OL,21,Fbattle the high prison population.
