OL,3,CHundreds of prisoners released early
OL,4,Cin Scotland
OL,6,FShe said those being released were
OL,7,Fserving a "wide range" of sentences,
OL,8,Fincluding for violent crimes and
OL,9,Fcrimes of dishonesty.
OL,11,FShe told the BBC's Good Morning
OL,12,FScotland programme: "It is fair to say
OL,13,Fthat in terms of crimes of violence
OL,14,Fthat is not an insignificant
OL,15,Fproportion of people serving short-
OL,16,Fterm sentences.
