OL,3,CHundreds of prisoners released early
OL,4,Cin Scotland
OL,6,F"But the important point, and the
OL,7,Fraison d'etre of this legislation, is
OL,8,Fthat we need to achieve a sustained
OL,9,Freduction in the prison population
OL,10,Fthat is necessary to ensure that our
OL,11,Fprisons can continue to accommodate
OL,12,Fthose who pose the greatest risk of
OL,13,Fharm, and also to support
OL,14,Frehabilitation in order to reduce re-
OL,15,Foffending.
OL,17,F"There is an inextricable link between
OL,18,Fthe work that goes on in prisons and
OL,19,Fthe safety of our community."
