OL,3,CHundreds of prisoners released early
OL,4,Cin Scotland
OL,6,FPrison bosses have warned of "critical
OL,7,Fchallenges" as result of the rising
OL,8,Fnumbers of inmates.
OL,10,FLast year, First Minister John Swinney
OL,11,Fsaid that prisons were "absolutely
OL,12,Fbursting at the seams" with more than
OL,13,F8,300 people behind bars - above the
OL,14,Foperating capacity of 8,007.
OL,16,FMore than 450 prisoners were released
OL,17,Fearly as part of an emergency move to
OL,18,Fease overcrowding in the summer of
OL,19,F2024. Dozens of those prisoners went
OL,20,Fon to re-offend and ended up back
OL,21,Fbehind bars.
