OL,4,Cin Scotland
OL,6,FPrisons continued to struggle with
OL,7,Fovercrowding again, within months of
OL,8,Fthat release scheme.
OL,10,FThe Justice Secretary said these
OL,11,Fcurrent measures would result in an
OL,12,F"immediate and sustained reduction" in
OL,13,Fprison population, while previous
OL,14,Freleases only provided "temporary
OL,15,Frespite".
